"title": "5004: human race, and sin",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5004: human race, and sin",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>As a result of the fall, human beings have become separated from God through sin, and are divided amongst themselves. All are in a condition of spiritual blindness, slavery and death, and are incapable of saving themselves from this situation.</p>\n<h2>All the human race is sinful</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:9-Rom3:12\">ROM 3:9–3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:1-Ps14:3\">PSA 14:1–14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps53:1-Ps53:3\">PSA 53:1–53:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5-Gen6:13\">GEN 6:5–6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:14-Job15:16\">JOB 15:14–15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:20\">ECC 7:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom1:32\">ROM 1:18–1:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:1-Rev18:5\">REV 18:1–18:5</a> <em>Babylon symbolises human society which in its opposition to God has become thoroughly corrupt.</em></p>\n<h2>The human race is estranged from God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:1-Isa59:2\">ISA 59:1–59:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:8-Gen3:10\">GEN 3:8–3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:22-Gen3:24\">GEN 3:22–3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:4-Ps5:5\">PSA 5:4–5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:12\">EPH 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:17-Eph4:18\">EPH 4:17–4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:21\">COL 1:21</a></p>\n<h2>The human race is spiritually callous, blind, enslaved and dead</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1-Eph2:3\">EPH 2:1–2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:17-Eph4:19\">EPH 4:17–4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21\">ROM 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12-Rom5:14\">ROM 5:12–5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:16-Rom6:20\">ROM 6:16–6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:19\">1JN 5:19</a></p>\n<h2>The human race is divided</h2>\n<h3>The human race is divided individual against individual</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:3-Gen4:9\">GEN 4:3–4:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:28-Rom1:29\">ROM 1:28–1:29</a></p>\n<h3>The human race is divided man against woman</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:8-Gen3:12\">GEN 3:8–3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:16\">GEN 3:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:9\">PRO 21:9</a></p>\n<h3>The human race is divided nation against nation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:1-Gen11:9\">GEN 11:1–11:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:6-Matt24:7\">MAT 24:6–24:7</a></p>\n<h3>The human race is divided Jew against Gentile</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:27-Acts10:28\">ACT 10:27–10:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:11-Eph2:12\">EPH 2:11–2:12</a></p>\n<h3>The human race is divided rich against poor</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:4-Amos8:6\">AMO 8:4–8:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:7\">JAS 2:1–2:7</a></p>\n<h2>The human race has been weakened by sin</h2>\n<h3>The human race has become subject to death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:16-Gen2:17\">GEN 2:16–2:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">ROM 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:21\">1CO 15:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:15\">JAS 1:15</a></p>\n<h3>Human beings have become weak and frail</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:6-Isa40:7\">ISA 40:6–40:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:1-Job14:12\">JOB 14:1–14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:3-Ps90:6\">PSA 90:3–90:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13-Ps103:16\">PSA 103:13–103:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:1-Eccl12:7\">ECC 12:1–12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:24-1Pet1:25\">1PE 1:24–1:25</a></p>",
